# Cline AI Rules

## Project Overview

**Claude NextJS Starters** - A production-ready Next.js 16 starter kit.

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 16.1.1 (App Router) + React 19
- TypeScript 5 (strict mode)
- Tailwind CSS v4 (OKLCH color system)
- shadcn/ui (New York style) + Radix UI
- lucide-react icons
- next-themes (dark/light mode)

